fields.name: Team 1
fields.description:
We are a small, dedicated team. From our headquarters in Central Switzerland we overlook Lake Zurich. In our daily business we coordinate production facilities and take care of our customer's requests.
Swiss precision and hands-on approach are part of our trademark. Passion for yarns of excellence and passion in life define us.
